name: r-gwpcr

owner.description: Bioconda is a distribution of bioinformatics software realized as a channel for the versatile Conda package manager.
owner.name: bioconda

summary: Implements the necessary distributions and parameter estimation procedures for a model of amplification and high-troughput sequencing. The model is based on a mechanistic model of PCR amplification as a Galton-Watson branching process, and on Poissonan sampling to model high-throughput sequencing.
